{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Devrsi0n","author":"Devrsi0n"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"0eee357f-fe74-52b8-834b-5e86116096f1","html":"<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/df136bd8e8275104fcdc7ab648eb40b5/c25da/font.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 50.23310023310024%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"font\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/df136bd8e8275104fcdc7ab648eb40b5/623ee/font.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/df136bd8e8275104fcdc7ab648eb40b5/816c5/font.png 148w,\n/static/df136bd8e8275104fcdc7ab648eb40b5/c766b/font.png 295w,\n/static/df136bd8e8275104fcdc7ab648eb40b5/623ee/font.png 590w,\n/static/df136bd8e8275104fcdc7ab648eb40b5/e5345/font.png 885w,\n/static/df136bd8e8275104fcdc7ab648eb40b5/7a439/font.png 1180w,\n/static/df136bd8e8275104fcdc7ab648eb40b5/c25da/font.png 1716w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>头图来自<a href=\"https://source.typekit.com/source-han-serif/cn/\">思源宋体</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>作为一名前端工程师，经常在还原设计师视觉稿时忽略字体，其实选择一套精心设计过的字体能极大地提升产品的视觉感受。今天就从这个很容易被忽略的细节入手，Web 开发需要了解的字体相关知识都梳理一遍。然而不像拉丁语系翻来覆去就那么一点西文字符，常见的字体就 100+ KB，而中文字体要包含常用汉字动辄 10+ MB 的体积（比如，著名的 <a href=\"https://github.com/adobe-fonts/source-han-sans/tree/release\">思源黑体</a> 光常规字重就高达 23 MB）实在不适合内嵌到 Web。</p>\n<p>所以常见的做法都是选择操作系统自带的字体。一般放多套字体按顺序渲染，若第一个字体操作系统已安装即可渲染，未安装则尝试渲染第二个字体，以此类推直至所有字体尝试渲染都失败的话就回退（fallback）到浏览器默认字体。</p>\n<p><strong>注意</strong>，一般把西文字体放在中文字体之前，因为中文字体自带了西文，但是效果一般不太好。</p>\n<p>比如下面这段 CSS 代码就是 GitHub 的字体样式。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">body</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif,\n    Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>字体一般分为衬线字体（Serif）和无衬线字体（Sans-Serif），它们有什么区别？</p>\n<h2 id=\"serif-vs-sans-serif\"><a href=\"#serif-vs-sans-serif\" aria-label=\"serif vs sans serif permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Serif VS Sans-Serif</h2>\n<p>在字体排印学里，衬线指的是字母结构笔画之外的装饰性笔画。有衬线的字体叫衬线体（serif），也叫“白体”；没有衬线的字体，则叫做无衬线体（sans-serif），相对的也叫“黑体”。维基百科这 2 张图一目了然。</p>\n<h3 id=\"西文\"><a href=\"#%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%87\" aria-label=\"西文 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>西文</h3>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2d659bdb967fcfff796a9c4fd9c608d4/0e3c2/serif-and-sans-serif.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 513px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 55.165692007797276%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"serif and sans serif\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/2d659bdb967fcfff796a9c4fd9c608d4/0e3c2/serif-and-sans-serif.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2d659bdb967fcfff796a9c4fd9c608d4/344b8/serif-and-sans-serif.png 148w,\n/static/2d659bdb967fcfff796a9c4fd9c608d4/52f2b/serif-and-sans-serif.png 295w,\n/static/2d659bdb967fcfff796a9c4fd9c608d4/0e3c2/serif-and-sans-serif.png 513w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 513px) 100vw, 513px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h2 id=\"中文\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87\" aria-label=\"中文 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>中文</h2>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/22aba87fe8f29844b682ca2035441e32/dce3f/serif-and-sans-serif-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 348px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 134.48275862068965%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"serif and sans serif 2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/22aba87fe8f29844b682ca2035441e32/dce3f/serif-and-sans-serif-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/22aba87fe8f29844b682ca2035441e32/56e59/serif-and-sans-serif-2.png 148w,\n/static/22aba87fe8f29844b682ca2035441e32/56c8e/serif-and-sans-serif-2.png 295w,\n/static/22aba87fe8f29844b682ca2035441e32/dce3f/serif-and-sans-serif-2.png 348w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 348px) 100vw, 348px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Serif 的字体容易辨认，因此易读性较高。反之 Sans Serif 则较醒目，但在行文阅读的情況下，Sans-Serif 容易造成字母辨认的困扰，常会有来回重读及上下行错乱的情形。</p>\n<p>Serif 强调了字母笔画的开始及结束，因此较易前后连续性的辨识。\nSerif 强调一个 word，而非单一的字母，反之 Sans-Serif 则强调个别字母。</p>\n<p>在小字体的场合，通常 Sans-Serif 比 Serif 更清晰。</p>\n<h3 id=\"结论\"><a href=\"#%E7%BB%93%E8%AE%BA\" aria-label=\"结论 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>结论</h3>\n<p>一般在正文里使用 Serif，显示效果较为工整，但注意字体不能设置的过小，Serif 在高分屏显示效果最佳，建议非高分屏使用 Sans Serif 字体。标题和除正文之外的地方适合用 Sans Serif，较为醒目和易辨识。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>下面这段代码可用于检测高分屏</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">isHighDensity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">typeof</span> window <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`undefined`</span></span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>matchMedia <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchMedia</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">'only screen and (min-resolution: 124dpi), only screen and (min-resolution: 1.3dppx), only screen and (min-resolution: 48.8dpcm)'</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>matches <span class=\"token operator\">||</span>\n        window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchMedia</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n          <span class=\"token string\">'only screen and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.3), only screen and (-o-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.6/2), only screen and (min--moz-device-pixel-ratio: 1.3), only screen and (min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.3)'</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>matches<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>devicePixelRatio <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>devicePixelRatio <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">1.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>下面按非衬线和衬线字体划分，介绍一些操作系统自带的较美观的字体。</p>\n<h2 id=\"sans-serif-非衬线字体\"><a href=\"#sans-serif-%E9%9D%9E%E8%A1%AC%E7%BA%BF%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93\" aria-label=\"sans serif 非衬线字体 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Sans-Serif 非衬线字体</h2>\n<p>Sans-Serif 字体清晰可辨，一般操作系统默认字体也是 Sans-Serif，相比 Serif 选择较多。</p>\n<h3 id=\"macos\"><a href=\"#macos\" aria-label=\"macos permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>macOS</h3>\n<h4 id=\"pingfang-苹方\"><a href=\"#pingfang-%E8%8B%B9%E6%96%B9\" aria-label=\"pingfang 苹方 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PingFang 苹方</h4>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2408d59b0fa8b12eb24227b9986c4c18/7b8c6/pingfang.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 13.432835820895523%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"pingfang\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/2408d59b0fa8b12eb24227b9986c4c18/44e84/pingfang.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2408d59b0fa8b12eb24227b9986c4c18/68355/pingfang.jpg 148w,\n/static/2408d59b0fa8b12eb24227b9986c4c18/ada22/pingfang.jpg 295w,\n/static/2408d59b0fa8b12eb24227b9986c4c18/44e84/pingfang.jpg 590w,\n/static/2408d59b0fa8b12eb24227b9986c4c18/7b8c6/pingfang.jpg 871w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>PingFang 是 mac 系统自 OS X EL Capitan(10.11)自带的字体，字体清晰锐利。</p>\n<h4 id=\"hiragino-sans-gb-冬青黑体\"><a href=\"#hiragino-sans-gb-%E5%86%AC%E9%9D%92%E9%BB%91%E4%BD%93\" aria-label=\"hiragino sans gb 冬青黑体 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hiragino Sans GB 冬青黑体</h4>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6df96161bf8c5bf5e32475b2c378bf28/bc7d5/hiragino.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  