Hei\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/beccebc23dbec373bd614254d40cd11a/623ee/wenquanyi-microhei.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/beccebc23dbec373bd614254d40cd11a/816c5/wenquanyi-microhei.png 148w,\n/static/beccebc23dbec373bd614254d40cd11a/c766b/wenquanyi-microhei.png 295w,\n/static/beccebc23dbec373bd614254d40cd11a/623ee/wenquanyi-microhei.png 590w,\n/static/beccebc23dbec373bd614254d40cd11a/ef4d4/wenquanyi-microhei.png 600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>文泉驿微米黑是 Linux 上较为常见的高质量中文非衬线字体。</p>\n<h2 id=\"serif-衬线字体\"><a href=\"#serif-%E8%A1%AC%E7%BA%BF%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93\" aria-label=\"serif 衬线字体 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Serif 衬线字体</h2>\n<p>各操作系统下优美的 Serif 字体选择较少，选择典型字体讲解。</p>\n<h3 id=\"macos-1\"><a href=\"#macos-1\" aria-label=\"macos 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>macOS</h3>\n<h4 id=\"songti--stsong\"><a href=\"#songti--stsong\" aria-label=\"songti  stsong permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Songti &#x26; STSong</h4>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b315dc2d48f056973635503ea8691ee2/82710/songti-sc%26stsong.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 43.58108108108108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"songti sc stsong\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b315dc2d48f056973635503ea8691ee2/623ee/songti-sc%26stsong.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b315dc2d48f056973635503ea8691ee2/816c5/songti-sc%26stsong.png 148w,\n/static/b315dc2d48f056973635503ea8691ee2/c766b/songti-sc%26stsong.png 295w,\n/static/b315dc2d48f056973635503ea8691ee2/623ee/songti-sc%26stsong.png 590w,\n/static/b315dc2d48f056973635503ea8691ee2/82710/songti-sc%26stsong.png 592w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Mac 上的 Songti SC/TC 和 STSong 两款都是常州华文公司制作的「华文宋体」。2 款字体字型十分相近，但是 Songti